---
import SectionContainer from "./SectionContainer.astro";
import Briefcase from "./Icons/Briefcase.astro";
import Books from "./Icons/Books.astro";
import Experience from "./Experience.astro";
import Education from "./Education.astro";
---

<section class="pt-2 pb-6 lg:pt-[20px] lg:pb-[20px]">
  <div class="w-auto px-4 lg:w-[1140px]">
    <p class="mb-5 text-base text-body-color text-pretty">
      My name is Lorena â€“ originally from sunny Spain, but these days, you'll
      find me navigating the Scottish landscapes. <br /> My coding adventure goes
      way back to the 2010s, where I first dipped my toes into the world of HTML
      and CSS by tweaking Myspace and Tumblr themes. <br /> Back then, it was all
      about adding that perfect touch of aesthetic flair. <br />
      As I transitioned into adulthood, I carved out a career in media and design.
      It was a university project that brought me back to coding, reigniting a passion
